
```apache
# Proteger facturas
Order Deny,Allow
Deny from all
<FilesMatch "\.(pdf)$">
    Allow from all
</FilesMatch>

# Prevenir listado de directorio
Options -Indexes

# Solo permitir acceso desde dominio propio
SetEnvIf Referer "^https://automatizatech.shop" local_ref=1
Order Allow,Deny
Allow from env=local_ref
```